<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Join Us Application Received</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 35px 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #0066cc;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .info-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 25px;
      }
      .info-table td {
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        vertical-align: top;
      }
      .info-table td.label {
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 35%;
        color: #222;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #e8f3ff;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #004085;
        border: 1px solid #b8daff;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        padding-top: 15px;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>New “Join Us” Form Submission</h2>

      <p>
        Hello,<br /><br />
        A new applicant has just filled out the <strong>Join Us</strong> form on
        your website. Below are the details:
      </p>

      <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Company Name:</td>
          <td><%= name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Email Address:</td>
          <td><%= email %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <div class="highlight">
        Please review the applicant’s information and follow up if suitable.
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SAA Accounting. All rights
        reserved.
    
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
